      • findShortestPath

        Path findShortestPath​(java.lang.String startShortName,
                      java.lang.String endShortName)
        Finds the shortest path, by distance, between the two provided buildings.
        Parameters:
        startShortName - The short name of the building at the beginning of this path.
        endShortName - The short name of the building at the end of this path.
        Returns:
        A path between startBuilding and endBuilding, or null if none exists.
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if startBuilding or endBuilding are null, or not valid short names of buildings in this campus map.
